\c 16
\s Nhaka yaEfuremu
\p
\v 1 Zvino kwakabuda mujenya wevana vaJosefa kubva paJoridhani paJeriko kusvika pamvura yeJeriko kumabvazuva, kurenje uchikwira kubva paJeriko panyika yezvikomo yeBheteri\x + 8.15; 18.12,13.\x*;
\v 2 ndokubuda kubva paBheteri kuenda kuRuzi\x + Gen.. 28.19.18.13. Vato. 1.23,26.\x*, ndokupfuurira kumuganhu wevaArikiti kuAtaroti\x + 2 Sam. 16.10. 1 Makor. 27.33.\x*.
\v 3 Zvino wakaburukira nechekumavirazuva kumuganhu wevaJafireti kuenda kumuganhu weBheti-Horoni pazasi\x + 16.5; 10.10.\x*, uye kusvika kuGezeri\x + 16.10; 10.33.\x*; uye kubuda kwawo kwaiva pagungwa.
\v 4 Zvino vanakomana vaJosefa, Manase naEfuremu vakagara nhaka\x + 17.14.\x*.
\p
\v 5 Zvino muganhu wevana vaEfuremu zvichienderana nemhuri dzavo waiva \add wakadai\add*: Iwo muganhu wenhaka yavo kumabvazuva waiva Ataroti-Adhari\x + 18.13; 16.2,7; 1 Makor. 2.54.\x* kusvika Bheti-Horoni kumusoro\x + 16.3.\x*.
\v 6 Zvino muganhu wakabudira kugungwa paMikimetati kubva kumaodzanyemba\x + 17.7.\x*; muganhu ndokudzokera kumabvazuva paTanati-Shiro\x + 18.1.\x*, ndokupfuura napo kumabvazuva kuenda kuJanowa;
\v 7 zvino wakaburuka kubva paJanowa kuenda kuAtaroti nekuNahara, ndokugunzva Jeriko, ndokubudira paJoridhani\x + 1 Makor. 7.28.\x*.
\v 8 Kubva paTapua muganhu wakaenda kumavirazuva\x + 12.17; 17.8.\x* kurwizi Kana\x + 17.9.\x*, uye kubuda kwawo kwaiva pagungwa. Iyi inhaka yerudzi rwevana vaEfuremu zvichienderana nemhuri dzavo.
\v 9 Uye maguta aiva akakamurirwa vana vaEfuremu aiva pakati penhaka yevana vaManase, maguta ose nemisha yawo\x + 17.9.\x*.
\v 10 Zvino havana kudzinga VaKenani vaigara paGezeri\x + Vato. 1.29. 1 Madz. 9.16. Josh. 15.63. 17.12,13.\x*. Naizvozvo VaKenani vakagara pakati peVaEfuremu kusvika nhasi; asi vakava vabati vechibharo\x + Gen.. 49.15.\x*.